    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>As a Web Designer/Information Architect, I want a clear Information Architecture for mobile and desktop so that we meet the "Site Design" (10%) criteria.</p>



<ul>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> * Create a <b>Sitemap</b> and <b>User Flow</b> for the Login and Dashboard views.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria (UoG Alignment):</b>
	<ul>
		<li>Diagram clearly shows different paths for Students, Coordinators, and Admins.</li>
		<li>Documentation includes a "Non-Technical" description to prepare for Task 3 (the Presentation).</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

