    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>As a Scrum Master, I want to document our Sprint 1 Planning and Daily Standups so that we have evidence of "Agile methods followed" for the 10% assessment component.</p>



<ul>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> * Create a standardized "Meeting Minutes" template.
	<ul>
		<li>Document the <b>Sprint 1 Planning Meeting</b> (Attendance, Goals, Task Allocation).</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b>
	<ul>
		<li>Minutes include a list of team members, roles assigned, and key decisions made.</li>
		<li>Evidence of "Diverse Background" collaboration (Learning Outcome 1) is subtly highlighted in the meeting notes.</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

